LEDI.Name: Forseti II
LEDI.Message: This mighty keep serves as a grand battlefield, with plentiful weapons, and a good balance between open-area combat and architecture.  A good 2 player or more rumble.

LEDI.Name: Gefjon II
LEDI.Message: The spacious but intricate temple of Gefjon offers an excellent battleground for epic matches of skill and death-dealing.

LEDI.Name: Ragnarok II
LEDI.Message: Ragnarok's relatively small, enclosed deathdome offers close-quarter action, yet balances this with numerous cover areas and platforms.

LEDI.Name: Lemon Lender II
LEDI.Message: I do business in new, factory refurbished new, and used lemons.
